  "description": "<p>Job Title</p><p>Driver</p><p>Occupation</p><p>VAN DRIVER</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Job Title</strong><br />Driver - 10 PM to 10 AM (Night Shift Driver)</p><p><strong>Occupation</strong><br />Driver</p><p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong><br />We seek a responsible individual to join us as a Class 3 Delivery Driver.</p><p><em>(Roasted Meat Manufacturer at Bedok Industrial Area)</em></p><p><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Shift</strong>: 10 PM to 10 AM (Night Shift-working time will be adjust based on order)</li><li><strong>Days</strong>: 6 days per week</li></ul><p><strong>Main Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Meat packaging tasks</li><li>Perform assigned deliveries</li><li>Communicate with customers and collect payments</li><li>Undertake other tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Must possess a valid Singapore Class 3 driving license</li><li>Ability to speak both English and Chinese</li><li>Clean driving record for the past two years</li><li>Willingness to work on public holidays and weekends</li><li>Comfortable handling non-halal products (e.g., pork)</li><li>Comfortable working in an oily environment</li></ul><p><strong>Employment Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Annual leave: 7 days and above</li><li>One meal is provided per shift</li><li>Performance bonus</li><li>Free medical visits (capped) at partnered clinics</li></ul><p><strong>Remarks</strong><br />A company vehicle is not allowed to be driven home.</p>",
